  "text": "### Domain Lineage: Strata FxVanillaOption Type Family Graph\n\n#### 1. Core Joda-Beans Domain Classes (modules/product/)\nThe four fundamental domain classes form the base of the FxVanillaOption type hierarchy:\n- **FxVanillaOption** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxVanillaOption.java): Represents a vanilla FX option, a European-style financial instrument that provides an option to exchange two currencies at a specified future time.\n- **FxVanillaOptionTrade** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTrade.java): Wraps an FxVanillaOption with trade-specific information such as trade ID, counterparty, and settlement details.\n- **ResolvedFxVanillaOption** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/ResolvedFxVanillaOption.java): A resolved version of FxVanillaOption where all references have been resolved (e.g., date adjustments have been applied).\n- **ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade.java): A resolved version of FxVanillaOptionTrade with all references resolved.\n\n#### 2. Pricer Classes (modules/pricer/)\nFour pricer implementations support pricing calculations using different models (Black and Vanna-Volga volatility models):\n- **BlackFxVanillaOptionProductPricer** (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/BlackFxVanillaOptionProductPricer.java): Implements Black volatility model for option pricing on the product level.\n- **BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer** (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer.java): Implements Black volatility model for complete trade pricing including financial charges.\n- **VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionProductPricer** (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionProductPricer.java): Implements Vanna-Volga volatility model for product pricing.\n- **VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer** (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer.java): Implements Vanna-Volga volatility model for trade pricing.\n\n#### 3. Measure Calculation Classes (modules/measure/)\nFour measure calculation classes wire the pricers to the calculation engine:\n- **FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations** (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations.java): Provides multi-scenario measure calculations for FX vanilla option trades, implementing PV, PV01, currency exposure, and other risk measures.\n- **FxVanillaOptionMethod** (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionMethod.java): Enumeration defining the pricing method to use (Black or VannaVolga).\n- **FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction** (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction.java): Implements CalculationFunction to perform calculations on FX vanilla option trades for scenario analysis.\n- **FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations** (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations.java): High-level entry point for FX vanilla option pricing and risk measures.\n\n#### 4. CSV Plugin Loader (modules/loader/)\n- **FxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin** (modules/loader/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/loader/csv/FxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin.java): Implements TradeCsvParserPlugin and TradeCsvWriterPlugin<FxVanillaOptionTrade> to enable loading and serializing FX vanilla option trades from/to CSV format.\n\n#### 5. Dependent Class Embedding FxVanillaOption (modules/product/)\n- **FxSingleBarrierOption** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxSingleBarrierOption.java): Represents an FX single barrier option and contains an embedded FxVanillaOption field named 'underlyingOption' (line 59: `private final FxVanillaOption underlyingOption`). This class extends the FxVanillaOption functionality by adding barrier conditions and optional rebate amounts.\n\n#### Type Family Architecture\nThe FxVanillaOption type family follows a clear pattern:\n1. **Product Types**: FxVanillaOption → FxVanillaOptionTrade (adds trade context) → Resolved variants (with calendar/business day resolution applied)\n2. **Pricing Hierarchy**: Product-level pricers handle core valuation; Trade-level pricers add financial charges and trade details\n3. **Model Variants**: Black model (faster, standard) and Vanna-Volga model (smile-aware, for over-the-counter options)\n4. **Integration**: Measure classes wire pricers into the scenario-based calculation framework for comprehensive risk analysis\n5. **IO**: CSV plugin enables persistence and data interchange\n6. **Extensions**: FxSingleBarrierOption builds on FxVanillaOption by adding barrier protection/knockout features"
}

